{"tid":2428547,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚惠珠認為超區議席應取消　改由新興企業等人士取代","createTime":"2021-03-01T15:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T05:38:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"70b7687d1851edd178e69f19b01998eda2f66238","tid":2428547,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:36:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578195-20210301.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578195-20210301.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt11u%2BYei5PLor89YqF%2FSdhCs%3D&h=096301cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578195-20210301.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4747b84c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578195-20210301.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中央在深圳舉辦第二日座談會，就完善香港選舉制度及落實「愛國者治港」原則，聽取香港各界人士意見。<br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠在會後表示，區議會發展至現時在立法會，可以佔有5個區議會（第二）功能界別、俗稱「超級區議會」的議席，以及可參與行政長官選舉委員會，這並非起草《基本法》時的原意，認為應將有關議席取消，改由新興企業或對內地更有認識，可推動香港融入大灣區的人士取代。<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠說，有意見提及功能組別的選民登記資格問題，認為需要限制有關工會和團體，要有4至5年的服務紀錄，有進行招聘及納稅證明，並在相關組別有往績，以證明並非急忙登記成為功能組別的選民。"},{"pid":"ac2a1cbaed968f29705d509d55a3bcac1e6cae4b","tid":2428547,"uid":42804,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:53:01.000Z","msg":"即係益哂班中國商人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daaa92ea543137a037fd1e06d7856ad5fa85d42d","tid":2428547,"uid":329324,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"70b7687d1851edd178e69f19b01998eda2f66238","tid":2428547,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:36:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578195-20210301.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578195-20210301.htm%3Fs